room_title: Escape room "Chapel Kidnap" by Eerie Escape in Columbus
room_description:
You have taken a trip to attend a festival in Mexico. While there, you learn of a group of people known only as La Sombra (The Shadow) who use the festival as their opportunity to prey on unsuspecting tourists.
As the night continues, you begin to feel disoriented... then you all pass out. When you wake up, find yourself in a cathedral, not sure how you got there. The only thing you know for sure is that there is a timer that indicates you have only one hour to escapeâ€¦
